We are Allied Arab Trading Co. LLC., a UAE based conglomerate engaged in importing,
distribution, trading and after sales service of Plumbing materials, Sanitary Ware,
Pumping materials, Renewable Energy infrastructure and Water Treatment setups.
Since inception, the company has grown from strength-to-strength and expanded its
products offerings and service capabilities to cover a wide range of requirements
of the building and real-estate industry. Our clientele includes end-users, consultants,
designers and architects; who turn to us for innovative and high-quality products.